```plantuml
@startuml LouisvilleMetro_WazeCCPProcessor

actor User
participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "waze-data-api Lambda" as API
participant "Aurora PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "waze-data-download Lambda" as Downloader
participant "S3 Bucket" as S3
participant "waze-data-process Lambda" as Processor
participant "SQS Queue" as SQS
participant "waze-data-alerts-processing Lambda" as Alerts
participant "waze-data-jams-processing Lambda" as Jams
participant "waze-data-irregularities-processing Lambda" as Irregularities
participant "SNS Topic" as SNS

User -> APIGW: API Request (GET/POST)
APIGW -> API: Forward request
API -> DB: Query data
DB --> API: Return results
API --> APIGW: API Response
APIGW --> User: Display results

group Data Ingestion
    Downloader -> WazeCCP: Fetch data
    WazeCCP --> Downloader: Return JSON data
    Downloader -> S3: Store raw JSON
    Downloader -> SNS: Publish notification
end

group Data Processing
    S3 -> Processor: Trigger on new file
    Processor -> S3: Get file
    Processor -> SQS: Enqueue processing tasks
    SQS -> Alerts: Process alerts
    Alerts -> DB: Store processed data
    SQS -> Jams: Process jams
    Jams -> DB: Store processed data
    SQS -> Irregularities: Process irregularities
    Irregularities -> DB: Store processed data
    Processor -> SNS: Publish processing complete
end

@enduml
```